title: BARCODE MAKER 5.5
description:
This is Barcode Maker 5.5 ...
It does come with a crack that allow you to use it with no time restriction BUT you will have a watermark on the TIFF images that you generate ... 
One way to avoid the watermark is to generate your image, the paste it on the right column of the program, select it, copy it (control + c) and the paste it in whatever program you want (excel, word, photoshop, ...)
This generate almost any kind of barcode: EAN8 / UCC8 / EAN13 / UCC 13 / ISBN / SCC-14 / UPC A / UPC-12 / UPC-E / CODE 39 / CODABAR/ CODE 2 OF 5 INTERLEAVED

eNJOY AND SEEEEEEEEEEEEEEDDDD
